  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Push the boundaries of crime and justice in the open world! CODERED 911 allows you to step into an action world with 50vs50 massive clashes, exciting PvP fights and endless freedom. Be a criminal or a cop, choose your own path and experience a realistic crime experience by customizing your character and vehicles as you wish while performing tasks on a large map.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exciting battles await you at every moment with multiplayer clashes. In the open world map, every corner holds a new opportunity, a new danger at every moment. Experience a completely different experience by choosing the role of police or criminal. Develop your character with various crime elements, shape your strategies using each of them, or better yet, become a cop, stop crimes, bring justice to the city and dominate your opponents.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In realistic PvP fights, every decision you make can lead you to either victory or defeat. Not only customize your character, but also modify your vehicles as you wish and gain advantage in races or clashes. Buy your own house, explore the city with your luxury vehicles and live every moment freely in the world of CODERED 911.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become a guardian of justice or embrace crime.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516150/extras/4e3b0e47c83c603ed3bc9337a967f099.poster.avif?t=1752605033\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516150/extras/4e3b0e47c83c603ed3bc9337a967f099.webm?t=1752605033\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516150/extras/4e3b0e47c83c603ed3bc9337a967f099.mp4?t=1752605033\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Chase or be Chased!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516150/extras/eb3800a8cd9b546f9041db5e1c60033b.poster.avif?t=1752605033\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516150/extras/eb3800a8cd9b546f9041db5e1c60033b.webm?t=1752605033\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516150/extras/eb3800a8cd9b546f9041db5e1c60033b.mp4?t=1752605033\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> Intense Fights!</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516150/extras/ab5e5904a1e41ebc47d2934b988593e3.poster.avif?t=1752605033\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516150/extras/ab5e5904a1e41ebc47d2934b988593e3.webm?t=1752605033\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516150/extras/ab5e5904a1e41ebc47d2934b988593e3.mp4?t=1752605033\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Kill or be Killed!</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516150/extras/d93a0645144f9e60a122142766261807.poster.avif?t=1752605033\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516150/extras/d93a0645144f9e60a122142766261807.webm?t=1752605033\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516150/extras/d93a0645144f9e60a122142766261807.mp4?t=1752605033\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Push the boundaries of crime and justice in the open world! CODERED 911 allows you to step into an action world with 50vs50 massive clashes, exciting PvP fights and endless freedom. Be a criminal or a cop, choose your own path and experience a realistic crime experience by customizing your character and vehicles as you wish while performing tasks on a large map.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exciting battles await you at every moment with multiplayer clashes. In the open world map, every corner holds a new opportunity, a new danger at every moment. Experience a completely different experience by choosing the role of police or criminal. Develop your character with various crime elements, shape your strategies using each of them, or better yet, become a cop, stop crimes, bring justice to the city and dominate your opponents.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In realistic PvP fights, every decision you make can lead you to either victory or defeat. Not only customize your character, but also modify your vehicles as you wish and gain advantage in races or clashes. Buy your own house, explore the city with your luxury vehicles and live every moment freely in the world of CODERED 911.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become a guardian of justice or embrace crime.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516150/extras/4e3b0e47c83c603ed3bc9337a967f099.poster.avif?t=1752605033\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516150/extras/4e3b0e47c83c603ed3bc9337a967f099.webm?t=1752605033\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516150/extras/4e3b0e47c83c603ed3bc9337a967f099.mp4?t=1752605033\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Chase or be Chased!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516150/extras/eb3800a8cd9b546f9041db5e1c60033b.poster.avif?t=1752605033\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516150/extras/eb3800a8cd9b546f9041db5e1c60033b.webm?t=1752605033\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516150/extras/eb3800a8cd9b546f9041db5e1c60033b.mp4?t=1752605033\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> Intense Fights!</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516150/extras/ab5e5904a1e41ebc47d2934b988593e3.poster.avif?t=1752605033\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516150/extras/ab5e5904a1e41ebc47d2934b988593e3.webm?t=1752605033\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516150/extras/ab5e5904a1e41ebc47d2934b988593e3.mp4?t=1752605033\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Kill or be Killed!</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516150/extras/d93a0645144f9e60a122142766261807.poster.avif?t=1752605033\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516150/extras/d93a0645144f9e60a122142766261807.webm?t=1752605033\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516150/extras/d93a0645144f9e60a122142766261807.mp4?t=1752605033\" type=\"video